entries.title_d: The Dantooine station has hired you to pick up a delivery that was ment for them in the Lok system.
entries.title: Lok System: Pickup Cargo for the Dantooine Station
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Meet the freighter at its arrival location.
entries.quest_location_d: The meeting point is located in the Lok system.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the freighter and pick up the cargo. Then bring it back to the Dantooine station.
entries.hello_d: Go ahead and dock whenever you are ready. We have the cargo.
entries.found_loc_d: Sending you the location of where we are supposed to meet the shipping company.
entries.failed_destroyed: How could you do that? They are never going to help us again.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Transferring cargo to your vessel. Make sure that Dantooine gets that shipment.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Ok, you have the goods Dantooine ordered. We are out of here.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Stand by. The shipping company said they would meet us here.
